description: This common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 58, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 116, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 8 for East, Box for South, and Leverage for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [116 Votes, Common]
